---
import Finance from "@/assets/Finance.astro";
---

<section
  class="mt-24 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl pb-12 px-4 items-center lg:flex md:px-8"
>
  <div class="space-y-4 flex-1 sm:text-center lg:text-left">
    <h1 class="text-white font-bold text-4xl xl:text-5xl">
      Bienvenido a tu
      <br />
      <span class="text-[#FAD961]"> Coperativa Impulsa</span>
      somos tu mejor opción
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-xl leading-relaxed sm:mx-auto lg:ml-0">
      En Impulsa, nos preocupamos por ti y tu familia, por eso te ofrecemos los
      mejores servicios financieros, para que puedas cumplir tus sueños y metas.
    </p>
    <div
      class="pt-10 items-center justify-center space-y-3 sm:space-x-6 sm:space-y-0 sm:flex lg:justify-start"
    >
      <a
        href="javascript:void(0)"
        class="px-7 py-3 w-full bg-slate-100 text-gray-800 hover:bg-slate-200 hover:text-gray-900 hover:scale-105 transition-all text-center rounded-md shadow-md block sm:w-auto"
      >
        Saber más
      </a>
      <a
        href="javascript:void(0)"
        class="px-7 py-3 w-full bg-[#FAD961] hover:scale-105 transition-all text-slate-800 text-center rounded-md block sm:w-auto"
      >
        Pide tu credito
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1 text-center mt-7 lg:mt-0 lg:ml-3">
    <Finance class="img" />
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .img {
    mask-image: linear-gradient(black 80%, transparent);
  }
</style>
